{"tid":2316896,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前男友與父親結婚 女兒大方捐卵：希望他們育有更多孩子","createTime":"2020-12-08T07:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T08:13:24.000Z","uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ceed8c49a6fd155f93b3bf2c0de6f9ac45460912","tid":2316896,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"英國首對合法同性夫妻巴里．德魯伊特．巴洛（Barrie Drewitt-Barlow）與前夫托尼（Tony）離婚後，與女兒的前男友丈夫斯科特．哈奇森（Scott Hutchison）於今年8月結婚共偕連理。其女兒提出捐卵，讓父親與前男友有更多的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n據英媒《每日郵報》報道，Scott比50歲的Barrie小25年，是一名雙性戀者，他在和Barrie 結婚前，曾與其女兒塞弗隆（Saffron）交往過3個月。<br />\n<br />\nBarrie和Scott於今年8月在克羅地亞島赫瓦爾（Hvar）一輛遊艇上訂婚，二人其後已透過代孕育一名女兒。近日Saffron在接受雜誌訪問時表示，很高興父親與Scott為對方找到幸福。她表示願意通過捐卵來幫助他們擁有更多孩子：「我很喜歡他們代孕的女兒瓦倫蒂娜（Valentina），我願意捐卵來讓他們育有更多孩子。」<br />\n<br />\nBarrie指，非常感謝女兒的心意，惟考慮到輩分問題，暫不考慮接受此好意。<br />\n<br />\nBarrie和他的前伴侶Tony在1999年成為第一對通過正式註冊的同性伴侶，當時一度成為新聞話題人物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/a5781340d615d95dfcff672b637d180f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201207/_2020120721215766602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fa5781340d615d95dfcff672b637d180f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201207%2F_2020120721215766602.jpg&h=8a78e9b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a7ac01bb71443f73e29c50a53008db83936ed0b","tid":2316896,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a065eabf7ed4541c7bdd6465e79d570e252be4","tid":2316896,"uid":156542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"咁撚複雜嘅"},{"pid":"1642a77256ccbf4511a3b0781bc93df79e633915","tid":2316896,"uid":41157,"like":1,"